Package: riboTransVis
Title: Visualize Transcript-Specific Ribosome Profiling and RNA-Seq Data
Version: 0.0.2
Author: Jun Zhang
Maintainer: Jun Zhang <3219030654@stu.cpu.edu.cn>
Description: The `riboTransVis` package provides tools for creating transcript-level analysis and 
  visualizations of ribosome profiling and RNA-seq data. It supports coverage plots, ribosome occupancy 
  normalization, and transcript annotation visualization, enabling in-depth analysis and 
  interpretation of ribosome and RNA signals. 
  Built on `ggplot2`, the package allows high-quality and customizable visualizations for 
  transcriptomics research.
License: GPL (>= 3)
